-- Merkel Welcomes Israeli Decision to Ease Gaza Blockade, Urges Fast Action
-- Alan Crawford
-- 2010-06-21T09:39:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-21/merkel-welcomes-israeli-decision-to-ease-gaza-blockade-urges-fast-action.html

          
          
             German Chancellor Angela Merkel
welcomes the decision by the Israeli Cabinet to ease the
blockade of the Hamas-ruled Gaza Strip, government spokesman
Christoph Steegmans said.  
 The German government urges a quick implementation of the
decision, Steegmans told reporters in Berlin today.  
          
          


  


        